{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Incredible acceleration and flexibility... Like it was designed specifically for space combat...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Why do the Forsakens have such an advanced frame?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Babylonia would design more advanced frames for Constructs with outstanding performance to further enhance their abilities.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "You must've heard of that tradition.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "Babylonia...? If that's the case, the only possibility is, from when you were still in Babylonia...", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: "Correct. It's got great performance but isn't really new.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "As to how I got it... I don't think I need to report to your commandant about that, do I?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'I think you should report it to me...', 3: '14', 4: "I guess you don't need to.", 5: '15'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "It's just only one of the normal conditions for my agreement.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Your commandant said no need to.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Never thought we would fight side by side again.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Same here.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: '...Why are you here, Watanabe?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Are you worried that I may do something to trigger the conflict between the Forsakens and Babylonia again?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'I made a deal with those hypocrites.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: "At least for now, we're using each other.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'Happy with my answer?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: "But helping you here isn't part of my agreement. I'm doing it for free.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: "What's your purpose then?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: "Can't it be just sympathy?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Watanabe', 3: "...Alright, I'll cut straight to the point.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Watanabe', 3: 'An Ascendant has already landed on the space station.', 4: '1'}
